-= HOW TO COMPILE =-

NOTE: Before executing the following commands, you need to download, compile, and install argos3: https://github.com/ilpincy/argos3

For simulation:

$ cd argos3-epuck
$ mkdir build_simepuck
$ cd build_simepuck
$ cmake ../src
$ make
$ sudo make install

If you wish to load the library without installing:
$ export ARGOS_PLUGIN_PATH=build_simepuck/plugins/robots/e-puck

For the real robot, after installing the cross compilation tool (detailed instructions in doc/installation.pdf):

$ cd argos3-epuck
$ mkdir build_realepuck
$ cd build_realepuck
$ cmake -DCMAKE_TOOLCHAIN_FILE=../src/cmake/TargetEPuck.cmake ../src
$ make
$ sudo make install
